VoiceDir65.8DD12: Elias starts laughing, mocking and sinister. Voices of the Tree soon laugh with him.
Line11.6D03F: While we stand here in the mud, Lilith is on her way to absorb Mephisto’s power. She has found a gateway to Hell, and she approaches with the key.
VoiceDir5.7FA05: Shock. Angry. Grief-stricken for his friend.
Line59.6DE47: The four of us, alone...this is lunacy.
Line5.7FA05: Worth the price? You owe the Tree your head! The day you die, you'll be taken to hang here with the others!

Line3.6D03F: Lilith has been two steps ahead of us for far too long. The Tree knew where to find her--I asked. Its answer was worth the price.
Line33.6DE47: Surely, there will be some resistance.
Line9.6D03F: And what, did I need your permission? It’s done. Put it aside.
